#~ "special \"^\") or last character in the set. <emphasis>s[eia]t</emphasis> "
#~ "matches <emphasis>set</emphasis>, <emphasis>sit</emphasis>, and "
#~ "<emphasis>sat</emphasis>, but not <emphasis>s</emphasis>o<emphasis>t</"
